## 📋 WORKSHEET STRUCTURE

### **📊 Sheet 1: Masterclass Overview**
```
Green Africa Hub - Masterclass Analytics
AI-Powered Advanced Learning Intelligence

MASTERCLASS DETAILS:
- Masterclass ID: [AUTO-GENERATED]
- Title: [TEXT]
- Level: [DROPDOWN: Beginner/Intermediate/Advanced/Expert]
- Duration: [HOURS]
- Start Date: [DATE PICKER]
- End Date: [DATE PICKER]
- Instructor: [TEXT]
- Focus Area: [DROPDOWN: Advanced Techniques/Cultural Preservation/Sustainability/Innovation]

AI CALCULATED METRICS:
- Learning Effectiveness Score: [AI SCORE 1-100]
- Cultural Transfer Rate: [AI PERCENTAGE]
- Skill Mastery Level: [AI RATING A-F]
- Teaching Quality: [AI SCORE 1-10]
- Community Impact: [AI SCORE 1-10]
```

### **📊 Sheet 2: Participant Analytics**
```
LEARNER TRACKING:
Participant ID | Name | Background | Baseline Skills | Progress | Mastery Level | AI Assessment

SKILL DEVELOPMENT:
- Technical Skills: [BASELINE] | [CURRENT] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [AI EVALUATION]
- Cultural Knowledge: [BASELINE] | [CURRENT] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [AI ASSESSMENT]
- Sustainability Awareness: [BASELINE] | [CURRENT] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [AI ANALYSIS]
- Innovation Capability: [BASELINE] | [CURRENT] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [AI INSIGHT]

AI LEARNING METRICS:
- Learning Velocity: =AI_LEARNING_VELOCITY()
- Skill Retention Rate: =AI_RETENTION_RATE()
- Mastery Prediction: =AI_MASTERY_PREDICTION()
- Personalized Recommendations: =AI_LEARNING_RECOMMENDATIONS()
```

